openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Isochrone
  description: https://github.com/punkerpunker/isochrone-api
  version: 0.0.1

paths:
  /isochrone: 
    get: 
      operationId: app.isochrone
      parameters: 
        - name: X 
          description: Longitude
          in: query
          schema:
            type: number
          required: true
        - name: Y
          description: Latitude
          in: query
          schema:
            type: number
          required: true
        - name: sec
          description: Seconds
          in: query
          schema:
            type: integer
          required: true
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Isochrone WKT polygon
          content: 
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  polygon:
                    type: string
